long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GitProfileScope is a Chrome extension that brings key GitHub user details to your browser in one simple view. Instantly access a user's number of repositories, stars, followers, following, commits, and more with a clean, intuitive display. Perfect for quickly assessing GitHub activity and influence at a glance.
